{"tid":1760422,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"哥倫比亞再發起全國罷工罷課 要求解散警隊兼悼念示威死者","createTime":"2019-11-28T08:02:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-28T08:09:20.000Z","uid":60545,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b77a63b6593dc3b693cebefe282fd38f4beec62d","tid":1760422,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T08:02:39.000Z","msg":"哥倫比亞工會及學生團體一周內第2次發起全國性罷工罷課，以悼念一名逝世的示威者，同時抗議貪腐、警察施暴和政府據傳將推行的經濟政策。<br />\n<br />\n數千名示威者在當地周三下午起，聚集在首都波哥大國會大樓外的中央廣場，有多達25萬人上街遊行及全國罷工。<br />\n<br />\n示威者群起反對當局可能延後退休年齡、降低年輕人最低薪資的經濟計畫，上周末警方鎮壓示威，觸發警民衝突，造成3人死亡，包括一名18歲示威者克魯茲（Dilan Cruz）被警方的催淚彈擊中後傷重不治，事件更令示威演變成更激烈的警民衝突。全國罷工委員會要求與政府代表對話，追究涉嫌濫暴的警員。<br />\n<br />\n示威者把克魯茲當成象徵人物，指控防暴警察驅散群眾時濫用武力。由主要工會和學生團體組成的全國罷工委員會（National Strike Committee）要求政府解散防暴警察部隊，並要求政府摒棄包括降低企業稅賦在內的稅務改革方案。<br />\n<br />\n杜克呼籲全國的民選省長及市長將與社會各階層對話以解決問題，但強調政府不允許暴力活動持續。杜克就任總統以來的16個月，政府問題連連，頻頻遭遇國會挑戰、支持率低落、推動立法失敗等窘境。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/hd.stheadline.com/amp/news/realtime/wo/1648636\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Famp%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fwo%2F1648636&d=gSA20A4kU26EBUHkB65AtKzbj60slk4H2lWqI%2F1XlBQ%3D&h=82fdda61\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/hd.stheadline.com/amp/news/realtime/wo/1648636</a>"},{"pid":"354c3ca46e78022f1c57ede6910d8c3142d01d17","tid":1760422,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T08:04:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c418e96faa73f48eccf15e825975a859bdf8a0cf","tid":1760422,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T08:05:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"218e5ccb3708f200db2851e928fb4f266c825892","tid":1760422,"uid":79117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T08:05:35.000Z","msg":"南美一浪接一浪，d五毛實話 CIA搞事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0edffe0d5ddda7ee448e5f5231e20ea4b219757","tid":1760422,"uid":103230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"218e5ccb3708f200db2851e928fb4f266c825892","tid":1760422,"uid":79117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T08:05:35.000Z","msg":"南美一浪接一浪，d五毛實話 CIA搞事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T08:07:51.000Z","msg":"其實老共唔明<br />\nd民眾冇怨氣就算有鬼挑撥都炒唔起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"804a01278c325f8200a0fad5ad5c6a7db85922b0","tid":1760422,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"218e5ccb3708f200db2851e928fb4f266c825892","tid":1760422,"uid":79117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T08:05:35.000Z","msg":"南美一浪接一浪，d五毛實話 CIA搞事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T08:08:01.000Z","msg":"廢腦乜都賴美國㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5038bfae77e1450d0f74183710a9ce1dfa0b59ca","tid":1760422,"uid":64071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T08:08:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a326405389eda2acb109b5b08c6bad6da92113c2","tid":1760422,"uid":66365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T08:09:01.000Z","msg":"香港罷課都仲要做功課，點解罷工唔洗攞啲野返屋企做呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a48a8a89fb83fc443b3d3047f6a0f134cc86c5c","tid":1760422,"uid":112581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b0edffe0d5ddda7ee448e5f5231e20ea4b219757","tid":1760422,"uid":103230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"218e5ccb3708f200db2851e928fb4f266c825892","tid":1760422,"uid":79117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"